        <h3>Making the first step</h3>
        <article>
          This journey started when I was a little boy curious about computers and technology. 
          When I was studying secondary school, my mom took me to a software academy center, 
          where I ended up spending all my three precious months of the summer time there. 
          I was in an introduction to computer and office software course. The course caught my interest. 
          From time to time, I became more interested in the new field ahead and amazed at how this whole thing operated on those computers. 
          After the summer break, I eventually had three certificates in office software, basic image editing on Photoshop, and basic web designing. 
          What a significant achievement for a 13-year-olds boy =)).
        </article>
